<% include ../partials/header %> 

 <div class="container" id="indexpage">
     <header class="jumbotron" id="indexjumbo">
         <div class="container" id="indexcontainer">
             <h1>Welcome To Touriste de Montreal!</h1>
             <p>Enjoy viewing so much of what this unique city has to offer. Montreal is a cultural hub that connects people from a myriad of different backgrounds harmoniously, embracing the diversity of its population and encouraging free and open expression.
             Known for it's historical Old Port district (the remnants of what was a major port in  19th and early 20th century North America), Montreal is also famous for it's innumerable festivals all through out the year, especially in the summer season. This makes Montreal a hotspot for tourists all around the world, and notably neighboring provinces and states, offering them an experience and setting that is equivalent to traveling half-way across the world.</p>
             <p>
                <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" href="/attractions/new">Add New attraction</a>
             </p>
         </div>
     </header>
     
     <div class="row text-center" style="display:flex; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <% attractions.forEach(function(attraction){ %>
            <div class="col-md-3 col-sm-6">
                <div class="thumbnail">
                   <img src="<%= attraction.image %>">
                   <div class="caption">
                       <h4><%= attraction.name %></h4>
                   </div>
                   <p>
                       <a href="/attractions/<%= attraction._id %>" class="btn btn-primary">See More Info</a>
                   </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        <% }); %>
    </div>
</div>

<% include ../partials/footer %>
